<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ880729-0052 </DOCNO><HL> Financing Business: Data-Design Laboratories Inc. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> DDL </CO><IN> BON </IN><TEXT>   DATA-DESIGN LABORATORIES Inc. said it sold $40.3 million of 8 1/2% convertible-subordinated debentures due 2008. Proceeds will be used to pay debt, for working capital and for possible acquisitions, the Cucamonga, Calif.-based maker of printed circuit boards said. Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc. is the underwriter. </TEXT></DOC>